title: Patient 001 with adenocarcinoma
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was extracted using the RNeasy kit (Qiagen, Valencia, CA), followed by treatment with DNase I. Double-stranded cDNA was synthesized from 500 ng of total RNA using MMLV-RT and poly dT primer incorporating the T7 promoter.
label_protocol_ch1: cRNA was generated and labeled with Cy3 or Cy5 (CyDye, Amersham Pharmacia Biotech, Piscataway, NJ) using the Low RNA Fluorescen
source_name_ch2: Total RNA from 20 lung cell lines representing all major histological types of lung cancers, labeled with Cyanine-3 (green).
extract_protocol_ch2: Total RNA was extracted using the RNeasy kit (Qiagen, Valencia, CA), followed by treatment with DNase I. Double-stranded cDNA was synthesized from 500 ng of total RNA using MMLV-RT and poly dT primer incorporating the T7 promoter.
label_protocol_ch2: cRNA was generated and labeled with Cy3 or Cy5 (CyDye, Amersham Pharmacia Biotech, Piscataway, NJ) using the Low RNA Fluorescen
scan_protocol: Whole Human Genome oligo DNA microarray with 41000 distinct probes was scanned using an Agilent DNA microarray scanner (G2505B, Agilent Technologies). Images were quantified using Agilent Feature Extraction Software (version 9.5).
data_processing: LOWESS normalized, background subtracted VALUE data obtained from ratio of processed Red signal/processed Green signal using GeneSpring software.

label_protocol_ch1: cRNA was generated and labeled with Cy3 or Cy5 (CyDye, Amersham Pharmacia Biotech, Piscataway, NJ) using the Low RNA Fluorescen
source_name_ch2: Total RNA from 20 lung cell lines representing all major histological types of lung cancers, labeled with Cyanine-3 (green).

label_protocol_ch1: cRNA was generated and labeled with Cy3 or Cy5 (CyDye, Amersham Pharmacia Biotech, Piscataway, NJ) using the Low RNA Fluorescen
source_name_ch2: Total RNA from 20 lung cell lines representing all major histological types of lung cancers, labeled with Cyanine-3 (green).
extract_protocol_ch2: Total RNA was extracted using the RNeasy kit (Qiagen, Valencia, CA), followed by treatment with DNase I. Double-stranded cDNA was synthesized from 500 ng of total RNA using MMLV-RT and poly dT primer incorporating the T7 promoter.
label_protocol_ch2: cRNA was generated and labeled with Cy3 or Cy5 (CyDye, Amersham Pharmacia Biotech, Piscataway, NJ) using the Low RNA Fluorescen
scan_protocol: Whole Human Genome oligo DNA microarray with 41000 distinct probes was scanned using an Agilent DNA microarray scanner (G2505B, Agilent Technologies). Images were quantified using Agilent Feature Extraction Software (version 9.5).

source_name_ch2: Total RNA from 20 lung cell lines representing all major histological types of lung cancers, labeled with Cyanine-3 (green).
extract_protocol_ch2: Total RNA was extracted using the RNeasy kit (Qiagen, Valencia, CA), followed by treatment with DNase I. Double-stranded cDNA was synthesized from 500 ng of total RNA using MMLV-RT and poly dT primer incorporating the T7 promoter.
label_protocol_ch2: cRNA was generated and labeled with Cy3 or Cy5 (CyDye, Amersham Pharmacia Biotech, Piscataway, NJ) using the Low RNA Fluorescen
scan_protocol: Whole Human Genome oligo DNA microarray with 41000 distinct probes was scanned using an Agilent DNA microarray scanner (G2505B, Agilent Technologies). Images were quantified using Agilent Feature Extraction Software (version 9.5).
data_processing: LOWESS normalized, background subtracted VALUE data obtained from ratio of processed Red signal/processed Green signal using GeneSpring software.
